    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become an adventurer and slay your way through infinite stages of enemies in this idle action RPG. Work your way through the hoards of creatures and beasts in order to bring back the glory to your village.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1117820/extras/e8f033d15ee77746c4bab75149cb79a9.avif?t=1747597887\" width=600 height=135 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's over 50 unique monsters with different variants and appearances to match each and every environment in which you will encounter them in. Paired with 25 different bosses and super bosses, you'll have your favorite monster to slay in no time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1117820/extras/d15bac12969bb5de3b9ad6fbe11a6357.avif?t=1747597887\" width=600 height=135 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect different armor and weapon sets in order to gain stat set bonus effects and other lucrative bonuses to help you along your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1117820/extras/b19481ffa54b63bc2245972a8adf8089.avif?t=1747597887\" width=600 height=135 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can't play the game all day? Then don't worry! Your progress will continue whilst you are offline, and you will come back to a whole host of loot and items when you make your return to vanquish more foes!</p>",
